---
import { SITE, WHATSAPP_LINK } from '../data/site';
---

<footer class="mt-8 border-t border-white/10 bg-[#0B1A2B]">
  <div class="mx-auto grid w-full max-w-6xl gap-8 px-4 py-12 md:grid-cols-3 md:px-8">
    <div data-reveal>
      <p class="text-xl font-black text-white">{SITE.brand}</p>
      <p class="mt-2 max-w-sm text-sm leading-relaxed text-slate-400">Automatizacion para clinicas en Colombia enfocada en mas citas por WhatsApp, mas conversion y mejor seguimiento comercial.</p>
    </div>
    <div data-reveal>
      <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-white">Contacto</p>
      <a href={WHATSAPP_LINK} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="mt-2 block text-sm text-slate-400 transition hover:text-[#25D366]">WhatsApp directo</a>
      <a href={`mailto:${SITE.email}`} class="block text-sm text-slate-400 transition hover:text-white">{SITE.email}</a>
      <a href={`tel:${SITE.phone.replaceAll(' ', '')}`} class="block text-sm text-slate-400 transition hover:text-white">{SITE.phone}</a>
    </div>
    <div data-reveal>
      <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-white">Enlaces</p>
      <a href="/servicios" class="mt-2 block text-sm text-slate-400 transition hover:text-white">Servicios</a>
      <a href="/como-funciona" class="block text-sm text-slate-400 transition hover:text-white">Como funciona</a>
      <a href="/casos-de-uso" class="block text-sm text-slate-400 transition hover:text-white">Casos de uso</a>
      <a href="/blog" class="block text-sm text-slate-400 transition hover:text-white">Blog</a>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="border-t border-white/10 px-4 py-4 text-center text-xs text-slate-400 md:px-8">(c) {new Date().getFullYear()} {SITE.brand}. Todos los derechos reservados.</div>
</footer>
